                <p>The summer research immersion typically runs from June to mid-August annually and is held at the
                    UTHSA Long School of Medicine campus in San Antonio. This year, the summer immersion will start on
                    June 5th and ends August 4th, 2023.</p>

                <div class="callout">
                    <p>Each scholar will receive a stipend contingent upon fulfillment of program completion as follows:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
